Speaker.P:
The following public appointments were made by my Department between 1 July and 30 September 2004. Enterprise Ireland: 
Ms Lorraine Benson, Department of Enterprise, Trade and Employment (26/07/04); 
Ms Margaret Daly, Operations Manager, Irish Environmental Service (Hazardous Waste Management) (17/09/04); 
Mr. Gerard O’Malley, Humans Recourses Solutions and Executive Search Consultancy (17/09/04). 
Shannon Development: 
Mr. Kieran Grace, Department of Enterprise, Trade and Employment and Mr. William Loughnane were reappointed by rotation to the board of Shannon Development on 6 July 2004. The reckonable date for both of them is 25 June 2004. 
Forfás: 
Mr. Eoin O’Driscoll, Managing Director, Aderra Consultancy Firm was appointed chairperson to the board on 13 July 2004. 
Science Foundation Ireland: 
Dr. Kristina Johnson, Dean of the school of engineering, Duke University, North Carolina, USA (reappointed 21 September 2004). 
Dr. Jane Grimson, Vice Provost, Trinity College, Dublin (reappointed 21 September 2004). 
