Ms Lucy Fallon Byrne, National Centre for Partnership and Performance. Irish Auditing and Accounting Supervisory Authority: 
Mr. Ian Drennan was appointed in July 2004 as chief executive officer designate to the Irish Auditing and Accounting Supervisory Authority, IAASA. 
